citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 3:00pm today. No
one answered the door knock and a phone call went to voice mail. Licensee was reached by text and informed inspector
that she wishes to cancel her license at this time as regulated activity is not currently being conducted. Inspector mailed
the licensee a cancellation form/cancellation instructions.
End Section
